<br>
&quot;Miriiam?&quot;<br>
<br>
Her hands shake as she wipes the tears from her cheek and tries to hide any sign that she was crying.<br>
<br>
&quot;Yea, Del?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;You ok?&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I'll be fine, Delshad. Don't worry about it&quot;<br>
<br>
Delshad rubs Miriiam's back and hugs her gently. &quot;Alright... Don't stay out here too long, its cold&quot;<br>
<br>
&quot;I won't&quot; Forcing a smile, she watches him leave. She wanted to cry out that everything wasn't all right, that nothing was, that she needed him here, needed anyone here. She wouldn't let herself trouble anyone else with her problems. Besides, Caelestis would be home soon. She could tell him everything, and if she couldn't, he would know anyways. Some how, Miriiam knew Caelestis would never come home soon enough... Nothing could come soon enough with her hating herself the way she did. She hated that her hair color wasn't her own, that her eyes matched her fathers, that her clothes weren't how she wanted; that she acted like everything would be ok when she knew it wouldn't. The only thing that could come soon was her release, and even that wouldn't be as soon as she needed it... <br>
 <p>Human. Something that god made. <Br> Eva. Something that humans made. <Br> Ayanami. Vessel of a soul. <Br> The power of Creation. <Br> The desire to become a God. <Br> -Neon Genisis Evangelion (the anime that has become my obessetion)</p><i></i></td></tr></table> </td></tr></table> <table border=0 width=95%><tr><td align=left valign="top"> </td><td align=right valign="top"><a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm6.showPrevMessage?topicID=15.topic"> << Prev Topic</a>&nbsp;| <a href="http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm6.showNextMessage?topicID=15.topic"> Next Topic >> </a><br><br><a self href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm6.showAddReplyScreenFromWeb?topicID=15.topic><img src=http://Auction.2y.net/user/paradisetheheretic/addreply.jpg border=0 alt="Add Reply"></a> </td></tr></table><br><table width=95% border=0><td valign="top"> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm6.emailToFriend?topicID=15.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/image/email.gif border=0 alt="Email This To a Friend"> Email This To a Friend</a><br> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm6.threadControl?topicID=15.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/professional/deleteThread.gif border=0 alt="Topic Control Image"> Topic Commands</a><br> <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm6.subscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/subscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to receive email notification of replies"> Click to receive email notification of replies</a> <br>  <a href=http://pub95.ezboard.com/ffantasystoriesforumfrm6.unsubscribeUnregisteredToTopic?topicID=15.topic><img src=http://www.ezboard.com/themes/ultimate/unsubscribe.gif width=20 height=20 border=0 alt="Click to stop receiving email notification of replies"> Click to stop receiving email notification of replies</a> <br> </td><td align=